(3090, 1, 'admin/aboutus/1', 'PUT', '116.75.209.63', '{\"name\":\"about us\",\"slug\":\"about\",\"companyprofiletag\":\"COMPANY PROFILE  THE GROUP (SINCE 1996)\",\"companyprofiledescription\":\"<div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>Ever since our foray began in 1964, RamaPly has made its mark as an eminent and trusted name in the Indian domestic panel industry. With an annual turn over of INR 700 Cr, we stand tall as the leading manufacturer of Steel, Film Face Shuttering Plywood, Flush Doors, Door Frames and Timber Trading in India. It is our consistent and dedicated efforts, along with innovative techniques and approach that spans decades that has resulted in the success of Rama Group of companies.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n <p>Rama Group of companies includes Rama Wood Crafts (ISO 9001:2008) and Rama Panels Pvt. Ltd. (ISO 9001:2008), with three business divisions: Wood Based, Iron and Steel and Timber. The state-of-the-art production facilities, dedicated research and development unit, able leadership and dedicated team are calibrated as a cohesive whole, to scale greater heights of success.<\\/p>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h5>Rama Wood Craft<\\/h5>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>Found in 1996, Rama Wood Craft is an ISO 9001: 2008 certified company that produces exceptional quality BIS certified products. The manufacturing plants are equipped with hi-tech machinery to ensure finesse in the final product. The plant is situated in Satna district of Madhya Pradesh which is renowned for rich hardwood. The chief products are different grades of plywood, block boards, flush doors and particle boards.<\\/p>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\\r\\n<h5>Rama Panels Pvt. Ltd.<\\/h5>\\r\\n<div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n<p>Established in 2007, Rama Panels has an ultra modern manufacturing facility in Rudrapur, Uttarakhand. It is an ISO 9001: 2008 accredited company with a plant that sprawls over 15 acres of land. Proximity to raw materials of the best quality ensures ease in procurement and production of the finest goods. All the products are certified by BIS and Forest Stewardship Council. The company is also a member of the Indian Green Building Council.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\",\"visionmissiontag\":\"Vision & Mission Taking Life Ahead\",\"missionvisiondescription\":\"<p>At Ramaply, we believe in innovating products that set a benchmark in the industry and offer maximum choice to the the discerning buyer. Our mission is to make finest quality products accessible at affordable prices and offer services that ensure hundred percent customer satisfaction.<\\/p>\",\"ourteamdescription\":\"<div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>Our team members are our greatest asset. Our ability to deliver outstanding results starts with our team of experts and their tenacity to work towards a common goal. As unique as we are individually, we share a mutual passion and doing excellent work, which has prompted the team members to work with us for an average of 10 years.<\\/p>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\",\"aboutushomedescription\":\"<h3>The Rama Group of companies is a leading member of the Indian domestic panel industry.<\\/h3>\\r\\n                <div class=\\\"text\\\">\\r\\n                    <p>Since the Group\'s inception, we have always planned for the future with a highly dedicated team and achieved our ambitious goals with the help of a hi-tech infrastructure and result oriented after sales service.<\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>We have marketing offices all over India.<\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>The Rama Group consists of two companies - Rama Wood Craft and Rama Panels Private Limited.<\\/p>\\r\\n                    <p>The unit is ISO 9001:2000 certified and is well reputed in the<\\/p>\\r\\n<p><a href=\\\"#\\\">\\u00a0\\u00a0Read More<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n                <\\/div>\",\"infrastructuretag\":\"Infrastructure Taking Life Ahead\",\"infrastructuredescription\":\"<p>We have two state-of-art facilities: in Satna district of Madhya Pradesh, and Rudrapur town of Uttarakhand. Both the units are located close to the sources of rich hardwood and best quality timber. The proximity creates ease in procurement of raw materials and production of final goods.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The facilities have modern and exclusively dedicated units that execute processes to deliver exceptional quality at each stage. Some of these units are: core veneer section, fork lift, cold press, calibrator, peeling machine, etc. The manual work is carried out by trained manpower under stringent supervision of techno-quality.<\\/p>\",\"_token\":\"lmfZUXohSps8CBQkzosT4g2tirWrY06GBqW5B2YR\",\"_method\":\"PUT\",\"_previous_\":\"http:\\/\\/ibeesmedia.com\\/ramaply\\/admin\\/aboutus\"}', '2019-08-30 12:09:13', '2019-08-30 12:09:13'),
