(1, 'Marine Plywood', 'Marine Plywood', 'test', 'marine-plywood', 'Marine Plywood', '<p>BIS certified Marine Plywood is a wood specialist that has been engineered by experts to give superior strength and durability.<br></p>', '<p style=\"line-height: 24px; color: rgb(91, 90, 89); font-family: Barlow, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">BIS certified Marine Plywood is a wood specialist that has been engineered by experts to give superior strength and durability. We believe in delivering the best quality exceeding the expectation of the customers.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>This is why we use strong Gurjan core which strengthens the ply from within. The individual veneers are bonded using undiluted Phenol Formaldehyde resin, and it keeps wood boiling water proof for 108 hrs. The bonding is done under high temperature and pressure to create flawless products of superior quality. Additionally, the ply is treated with anti-termite and anti-borer chemicals under Vacuum Pressure Impregnation which makes in resistant to insect attacks and gives it high load bearing capacity. </p>', '<ul>                          <li>BWP Grade: IS 710</li>                        </ul>', '<span style=\"font-family: \" open=\"\" sans=\"\" arial=\"\" sans-serif=\"\" text-align:=\"\" justify=\"\">It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. The point of using Lorem Ipsum is that it has a more-or-less normal distribution of letters, as opposed to using \'Content here, content here\', making it look like readable English. Many desktop publishing packages and web page editors now use Lorem Ipsum as their default model text, and a search for \'lorem ipsum\' will uncover many web sites still in their infancy. Various versions have evolved over the years, sometimes by accident, sometimes on purpose (injected humour and the like).</span>', 'productimage/Automotive.jpg', 'productimage/product detials.jpg', 'procuctbrochure/sphider-logo.png', 1, 1, '0', '2019-07-19 11:26:50', '2019-07-19 11:26:50', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(2, 'BWP Fire', 'BWP Fire', 'BWP Fire', 'bwp-fire', 'Automotive Ply', 'We care about the safety of our clients, which is why the quality of products, is a non-negotiable value for us.', 'We care about the safety of our clients, which is why the quality of products, is a non-negotiable value for us. This product is safe for both indoor and outdoor applications including buses and other vehicles. In fact, reputed Indian institutes like ARAI, ICAT, CIRT and BIS have certified the product. Additionally, Ministry of Belgium has certified the product with ECE R118 enabling the use of our plyboard in buses of European countries.', '<ul>\r\n\r\n<li>BWP grade: IS 710 and 15061, 5509</li>\r\n\r\n<li>BWP grade: IS 710 and 5509\r\n\r\n</li>\r\n<li>BWP grade: IS 710 and 15061 and 5509</li>\r\n\r\n</ul>', 'test', 'productimage/BWP & MR Blockboard.jpg', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, '0', '2019-07-02 13:28:57', '2019-07-02 13:28:57', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
